OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FFiona Cahill has spent decades trying
OL,7,Fto piece together the mysteries of her
OL,8,Fmother's childhood
OL,10,FAfter spending two years at
OL,11,FCastlepollard mother and baby Home in
OL,12,FCounty Westmeath, Ireland, which at
OL,13,Ftime had a 40% infant mortality rate,
OL,14,FMaria was adopted by a woman who she
OL,15,Fdescribed as "emotionally abusive".
