OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FFiona recalls how her mother would
OL,7,Fhave post traumatic stress disorder
OL,8,F(PTSD) symptoms stemming from her
OL,9,Fdifficult early years, and how the
OL,10,Ftrauma has been passed down the
OL,11,Fgenerations.
OL,13,F"She'd struggle controlling her
OL,14,Femotions," she said. "It could be
OL,15,Fchaotic and difficult growing up. We
OL,16,Fjust had to try to support her, but I
OL,17,Fjust remember feeling helpless."
