OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FMaria who lived in Doncaster and
OL,7,Fpassed away in 2023 aged 69, only
OL,8,Ffound out she was adopted when she was
OL,9,F21 as she applied for a passport.
OL,11,FIt wasn't until she was 40 that she
OL,12,Fdiscovered she was a British citizen
OL,13,Fafter finding out that she had two
OL,14,Fbirth certificates, a UK one and a
OL,15,F"falsified" Irish one.
OL,17,FIn the decades that followed she tried
OL,18,Funsuccessfully to trace her birth
OL,19,Fparents.
