OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,F"All she ever wanted was a hug from
OL,7,Fher own mum," Fiona said.
OL,9,FSince her mother's death, Fiona feels
OL,10,Fit's her duty to carry on the campaign
OL,11,Ffor justice and recognition.
OL,13,F"It's like a dark corner that never
OL,14,Fgoes away," she said. "One thing that
OL,15,Fcan't happen is for it to be swept
OL,16,Funder the carpet and forgotten, I
OL,17,Fcouldn't bare that thought."
