OL,6,FFiona has spent decades examining
OL,7,Farchives and files trying to piece
OL,8,Ftogether the mysteries of her mother's
OL,9,Fchildhood.
OL,11,F"There was an anti Irish migrant
OL,12,Frhetoric and the cost to the British
OL,13,Ftaxpayer is something that comes up a
OL,14,Flot in the archives," she said.
OL,16,F"They were justifying it about the
OL,17,Fcost. It was a real culture of shame,
OL,18,Fsecrecy and oppression.
