OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Conlon said
OL,7,Fhe had been "unaware" of the PFI
OL,8,Fforced repatriation scheme and
OL,9,Fdescribed it as "horrific".
OL,11,F'People want truth on the record',
OL,12,FLabour MP Liam Conlon, who is the
OL,13,Fnational chair of the Labour Party
OL,14,FIrish Society, told ITV News
OL,16,F"It's really shocking and a really
OL,17,Funderreported and unrecognised aspect
OL,18,Fof this wider scandal," he said.
