OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,F"To hear that women who would have
OL,7,Fbeen very vulnerable, who would have
OL,8,Fcome here (to Britain) to then be
OL,9,Fdeported, often very pregnant, and put
OL,10,Fin those institutions is horrific."
OL,12,FFiona and her family are now calling
OL,13,Ffor all archives from religious and
OL,14,Fstate run mother and baby institutions
OL,15,Fin the UK to be preserved and
OL,16,Faccessible.
OL,18,FShe wants a special site to house
OL,19,Fdocuments, objects and oral history,
OL,20,Fso that what happened cannot be
OL,21,Fforgotten.
