OL,6,FIn 2016 the head of the Catholic
OL,7,FChurch in England and Wales apologised
OL,8,F"for the hurt caused by agencies
OL,9,Facting in the name of the Catholic
OL,10,FChurch".
OL,12,FCardinal Vincent Nichols acknowledged
OL,13,F"the grief and pain caused by the
OL,14,Fgiving up of a child through
OL,15,Fadoption", and added that "the
OL,16,Fpractices of all adoption agencies
OL,17,Freflected the social values at the
OL,18,Ftime".
